---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-6 text-stone-100">About Pingus</h1>
  
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <p class="text-lg text-stone-300 mb-4">Hi! I'm Pingus (or Alex — same person!). I love making things with yarn.</p>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-stone-300 mb-4">This site is a collection of my crochet and knitting projects — some finished, some in progress.</p>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-stone-300 mb-4">I learned to crochet during the pandemic and have been hooked ever since. My favorite things to make are:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-300 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Amigurumi (crocheted stuffed animals)</li>
      <li>Cozy accessories (scarves, hats, mittens)</li>
      <li>Seasonal decorations</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-stone-300">Feel free to browse the projects, and if you have any questions about a pattern or want to chat, reach out!</p>
  </div>
</Layout>